<para>
  Enhance the &image; by minimizing noise.<footnote>
  <simpara>
	Sorry about the lack of documentation.  The ImageMagick
	documentation isn't very descriptive, and the source code
	simply says "EnhanceImage() applies a digital filter that
	improves the quality of a noisy image"
	[<filename>magick/enhance.c</filename>, in ImageMagick 6.1.8].
  </simpara>
</footnote>
</para>
<para>
  This routine comes from the <ulink url="http://www.imagemagick.org"
  role="external">ImageMagick</ulink> library.
</para>
